She cocked a brow. They were over another continent, far away from the base & 
he wanted to talk? She had to smile. Such spontenaity. She loved it. 

"Of course," she then turned to Blackstorm, "Blackstorm, take Sideways & the 
others & rendezvous with the Decepticons. I have to report to Hydras. I will 
join you all shortly." 

Without waiting for a reply, she dove into the forests of Western Africa 
below her, disappearing into the plush greenery. 

Landing with grace upon low hill, with a spectacular view. "Alright. I'm 
alone..." she stated, curious as to what he wanted.

--part1_185.1b963aa7.2c05a58f_boundary
